atement of reciprocity in terms of multivariate generating functions from\nwhich Stanley's result follows.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Apr 2003 18:18:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 20 May 2003 19:20:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
